snippet.title: Banjo Kazooie Grunty's Revenge (GBA) Longplay [175]
snippet.description: Sorry for the few skips in the video, i've been very sick so I couldn't do it all in one session, it took 2 while still feeling unwell. Anyways I play this game 99% blind, the 1% I didn't play blind was to find 2-3 spots to get 100% items. So yes I get every item in the game among completing it for the first time. The game is not bad, although I don't think this franchise translates to 2D that well. Still it's kinda fun and has good music/graphics. The hit detection is a little off sometimes unfortunately. The final boss is pretty annoying until I got the pattern down well enough.
